fr.cnrs.iees.graph.impl

Class ImmutableGraphImpl<N extends Node,E extends Edge>

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.cnrs.iees.graph.impl.ImmutableGraphImpl<N,E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Graph<N,E>, MinimalGraph<N>, fr.ens.biologie.generic.Sizeable, fr.ens.biologie.generic.Textable

    public class ImmutableGraphImpl<N extends Node,E extends Edge>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Graph<N,E>, fr.ens.biologie.generic.Sizeable, fr.ens.biologie.generic.Textable
    Implementation of an immutable Graph (no change in Nodes or Edges lists). Meant to be fast for searching by id. Edges are not stored in the graph as they are stored in the nodes.
    Author:
    gignoux - 6 sept. 2017
